                                    <name type="person" key="OlaHja001">Olafs b<ex>isku</ex>ps
                                        Hialltaſonar</name>, og hafdi fra alldaỏdle i involucrum
                                        in<ex>n</ex>ſaumad vered. detexi <name type="place" key="Copen01">Hafniæ</name>
                                    <date when="1725">1725</date>.</q>
                            </p>
